### Hadith 2:812

*Narrated 'Aisha:*

Safiya bint Huyay, the wife of the Prophet got her menses, and Allah's
Apostle was informed of that. He said, "Would she delay us?" The people
said, "She has already performed Tawaf-al-Ifada." He said, "Therefore
she will not (delay us)."

